   INFO: writing track 1 (ISO9660)...
   INFO: writing track 2, MPEG2, PAL 2/3 D-1 (480x576/25fps), audio[0]: l2/44.1kHz/224kbps/stereo ...
finished ok, image created with 816 sectors [00:10.66] (1919232 bytes)
<prompt>[madsdyd@ripley Avi 95%]$</prompt> <userinput>ls -l video.*</userinput>
-rw-r--r--    1 madsdyd  madsdyd   5519548 maj 28 20:52 video.avi
-rw-rw-r--    1 madsdyd  madsdyd   1919232 maj 28 21:01 video.bin
-rw-rw-r--    1 madsdyd  madsdyd       170 maj 28 21:01 video.cue
-rw-rw-r--    1 madsdyd  madsdyd    501984 maj 28 20:58 video.mpg
</screen>

